1
00:00:10,580 --> 00:00:11,380
Master.

2
00:00:12,980 --> 00:00:13,660
Where did you

3
00:00:13,900 --> 00:00:15,220
find this divine artifact?

4
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:17,260
This is no divine artifact.

5
00:00:17,900 --> 00:00:20,300
It is a treasure passed down
in the Shadow Clan.

6
00:00:20,980 --> 00:00:21,900
It contains

7
00:00:21,900 --> 00:00:24,700
a fiend born from the wicked thoughts
of the Three Realms.

8
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:26,900
It's called Xieyun.

9
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:31,780
The Shadow Clan has used this fiend
to enhance their power

10
00:00:32,220 --> 00:00:33,900
and oppose us.

11
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:36,860
I went to great lengths

12
00:00:37,060 --> 00:00:38,380
to acquire this.

13
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:40,900
From now on,

14
00:00:41,220 --> 00:00:43,060
you must guard it tightly.

15
00:00:43,860 --> 00:00:46,300
Do not let the Shadow Clan reclaim it.

16
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:50,100
[Records of the Immortal Venerables]
This book

17
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:52,180
contains information about Xieyun.

18
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:54,740
Take it

19
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:55,900
and have the disciples read it.

20
00:00:57,860 --> 00:00:58,660
Understood.

21
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:09,240
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 24]

22
00:01:38,660 --> 00:01:40,540
I used the power of the demon core

23
00:01:41,180 --> 00:01:42,740
to refine these pills for Wan'er.

24
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:44,700
Give her one

25
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:46,580
whenever her illness flares up.

26
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:49,940
Tomorrow,

27
00:01:50,300 --> 00:01:51,500
you will take her and leave.

28
00:01:52,100 --> 00:01:54,100
I'll take her far away

29
00:01:54,700 --> 00:01:55,660
so she

30
00:01:55,660 --> 00:01:56,900
won't be harmed by you again.

31
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:09,660
Wan'er.

32
00:02:09,660 --> 00:02:10,580
Let's go.

33
00:02:11,100 --> 00:02:12,300
He's not coming back today.

34
00:02:13,340 --> 00:02:14,340
I know Gu Li drove me away

35
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:15,660
to ensure my safety.

36
00:02:16,220 --> 00:02:17,740
I just wanted to say goodbye.

37
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:19,500
Yuxun,

38
00:02:19,860 --> 00:02:21,140
can you take me to see him?

39
00:02:21,140 --> 00:02:21,780
I...

40
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:23,660
I don't know where he is.

41
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:26,140
Wan'er, we need to go.

42
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:28,500
And, take this medicine with you.

43
00:02:29,780 --> 00:02:30,580
Miss,

44
00:02:31,100 --> 00:02:32,500
you're coming with me.

45
00:02:33,540 --> 00:02:34,180
Wan'er.

46
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:35,100
Run.

47
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:35,940
I'll hold her off.

48
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:36,500
Yuxun.

49
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:37,260
Run!

50
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,340
Overestimating yourself.

51
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:51,500
Wan'er.

52
00:02:54,460 --> 00:02:55,260
Wan'er.

53
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:56,940
Wan'er.

54
00:03:10,780 --> 00:03:11,540
Yaoyang,

55
00:03:11,780 --> 00:03:12,900
what are you doing?

56
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:13,700
Let me go!

57
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:14,740
Master,

58
00:03:15,780 --> 00:03:17,100
just one last step.

59
00:03:18,860 --> 00:03:20,300
Once Xieyun is transferred to me,

60
00:03:21,660 --> 00:03:22,860
I'll let you go.

61
00:03:24,060 --> 00:03:24,500
No.

62
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:25,580
Don't.

63
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:27,180
I am your master.

64
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:28,500
Listen to me.

65
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:31,340
I'm sorry.

66
00:03:33,180 --> 00:03:34,020
I can't listen to you

67
00:03:34,460 --> 00:03:35,580
on this one.

68
00:03:39,340 --> 00:03:39,820
Gu Li!

69
00:03:40,500 --> 00:03:41,180
Let me go.

70
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:43,100
Have you forgotten our deal?

71
00:03:44,540 --> 00:03:46,180
He's determined to save you.

72
00:03:46,940 --> 00:03:48,140
Besides, his Gu poison

73
00:03:48,340 --> 00:03:50,260
is beyond cure now.

74
00:03:52,380 --> 00:03:52,980
No.

75
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:54,140
Yang,

76
00:03:55,060 --> 00:03:55,900
trust me.

77
00:03:56,180 --> 00:03:58,100
I will find a way to save you.

78
00:03:58,340 --> 00:04:00,260
Let me go. Let me go!

79
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:03,380
Heng.

80
00:04:03,780 --> 00:04:04,540
Heng!

81
00:04:04,660 --> 00:04:05,420
Let me go.

82
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:09,740
Did you bring it?

83
00:04:16,700 --> 00:04:17,500
Heng,

84
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:18,580
are you

85
00:04:19,140 --> 00:04:21,100
just going to stand by
and watch Yang die?

86
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:24,300
Xiyin,

87
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:26,300
I'm sorry.

88
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:44,660
No.

89
00:04:44,980 --> 00:04:45,740
Don't!

90
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:47,100
No.

91
00:04:48,020 --> 00:04:48,900
Stop!

92
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:11,060
Yang!

93
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:18,820
Yang.

94
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:19,780
Yang.

95
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:21,460
Yang.

96
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:26,500
Master.

97
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:29,260
It's finally over.

98
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:31,580
Don't feel sad for me.

99
00:05:33,580 --> 00:05:34,540
My wish

100
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:36,460
is for you

101
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:38,100
to expel the fiendish aura within you

102
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:39,580
and get back to normal.

103
00:05:40,060 --> 00:05:41,180
I guess

104
00:05:41,180 --> 00:05:42,740
your wish is the same, right?

105
00:05:44,380 --> 00:05:45,500
Getting back to normal

106
00:05:46,580 --> 00:05:47,780
is never my wish.

107
00:05:49,140 --> 00:05:50,260
My wish is

108
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:53,700
to stay with you forever.

109
00:05:54,540 --> 00:05:55,300
It's just a pity...

110
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,580
Yang.

111
00:05:59,380 --> 00:05:59,940
No.

112
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:00,900
Yang.

113
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:03,500
Why wouldn't you listen to me?

114
00:06:04,540 --> 00:06:05,460
Trust me.

115
00:06:06,060 --> 00:06:08,060
I will find a way to save you.

116
00:06:08,860 --> 00:06:10,740
As long as you can live,

117
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:15,380
all my efforts and sacrifices

118
00:06:16,300 --> 00:06:17,380
are worth it.

119
00:06:18,740 --> 00:06:20,900
Now I can finally face my true feelings.

120
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:24,300
Towards my master,

121
00:06:25,740 --> 00:06:27,340
it was only gratitude.

122
00:06:30,580 --> 00:06:31,700
It's you I love.

123
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:35,540
Is it me?

124
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:36,100
Ruoxi.

125
00:06:47,340 --> 00:06:48,340
Well, well.

126
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:50,580
What a great show.

127
00:06:53,140 --> 00:06:54,140
What a shame.

128
00:06:56,780 --> 00:06:57,660
Heng,

129
00:06:58,540 --> 00:06:59,380
Xiyin,

130
00:07:00,340 --> 00:07:02,100
you two have really let me down.

131
00:07:03,140 --> 00:07:03,940
Immortal Venerable.

132
00:07:04,260 --> 00:07:05,900
I doubt you've told them

133
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:08,100
about all the things you've done.

134
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:09,660
She promised

135
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:11,540
not to harm the Shadow Clan again,

136
00:07:12,580 --> 00:07:14,260
yet she attacked me in secret.

137
00:07:14,900 --> 00:07:16,060
How despicable.

138
00:07:16,340 --> 00:07:17,940
Likewise.

139
00:07:18,900 --> 00:07:21,100
You also wanted to absorb Xieyun's power

140
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:23,540
through the Fushi Mirror.

141
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,060
I just

142
00:07:25,060 --> 00:07:26,100
beat you to it.

143
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:27,780
Immortal Venerable,

144
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:30,340
is what he's saying true?

145
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:32,700
Everything he said

146
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:33,780
is true.

147
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:36,100
Xieyun

148
00:07:36,700 --> 00:07:38,900
was born from the wicked thoughts
of the Three Realms?

149
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:42,940
That is a complete lie.

150
00:07:43,900 --> 00:07:44,820
Xieyun

151
00:07:45,780 --> 00:07:47,900
was born from her wicked thoughts alone!

152
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:50,060
As long as she's gone,

153
00:07:50,660 --> 00:07:51,580
Xieyun

154
00:07:53,020 --> 00:07:54,140
will disappear.

155
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:55,860
It's you.

156
00:07:56,740 --> 00:07:57,540
So

157
00:07:58,580 --> 00:08:01,100
