158
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:04,780
Why?

159
00:08:05,780 --> 00:08:07,060
You're already the Immortal Venerable.

160
00:08:07,340 --> 00:08:08,300
Why?

161
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:10,180
Now that you guys know,

162
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:12,700
I can't let you leave here alive.

163
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:14,620
Gu Li,

164
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:16,700
I brought you a little gift.

165
00:08:19,180 --> 00:08:20,100
Let me go.

166
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:21,740
What are you doing?

167
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:23,700
Hand over the Fushi Mirror.

168
00:08:24,220 --> 00:08:25,460
Gu Li, no!

169
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:30,580
Let Wan'er go.

170
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:34,980
Wan'er.

171
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:36,340
Wan'er.

172
00:08:36,900 --> 00:08:37,700
Wan'er.

173
00:09:00,180 --> 00:09:01,180
Hand over Xieyun.

174
00:09:03,780 --> 00:09:04,700
Don't hurt her.

175
00:09:05,300 --> 00:09:06,180
Xieyun is with me.

176
00:09:22,700 --> 00:09:23,500
No!

177
00:09:26,060 --> 00:09:26,860
Yang!

178
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:33,700
Yang.

179
00:09:35,580 --> 00:09:36,260
I

180
00:09:36,700 --> 00:09:37,940
