183
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:53,900
Yang!

184
00:09:54,700 --> 00:09:55,140
Yaoyang!

185
00:09:55,140 --> 00:09:55,780
Xiyin!

186
00:10:00,340 --> 00:10:01,420
Yang.

187
00:10:03,100 --> 00:10:03,900
Yang!

188
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:09,260
This one is you.

189
00:10:09,260 --> 00:10:10,260
And this one is me.

190
00:10:17,820 --> 00:10:18,620
Yang.

191
00:10:22,140 --> 00:10:23,100
Yang.

192
00:10:24,180 --> 00:10:24,580
Xiyin!

193
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:25,340
Yang!

194
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:37,980
Yang!

195
00:10:43,860 --> 00:10:44,660
Yang.

196
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:50,700
Yang.

197
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:53,540
Yang!

198
00:11:10,860 --> 00:11:12,420
Tanghulu!

